'''第149届[[牛津剑桥赛艇对抗赛|牛津剑桥赛艇对抗赛]]'''于2003年4月6日举行，裁判是牛津老将[[鲍里斯·兰科夫|鲍里斯·兰科夫]]。双方你追我赶，领先位置两度易主，最后牛津队以仅30厘米优势夺冠，是赛事历史上最小的胜出优势。比赛竞争激烈并获“史诗”美名，多次获奥运会金牌的[[史蒂夫·雷德格雷夫|史蒂夫·雷德格雷夫]]宣称这是“世世代代所见最精彩的比赛”。

[[牛津剑桥赛艇对抗赛|牛津剑桥赛艇对抗赛]]是[[牛津大学|牛津大学]]和[[剑桥大学|剑桥大学]]一年一度的[[赛艇|并排赛艇]]比赛，在西南伦敦的6.8公里[[泰晤士河|泰晤士河]]河道举行。本届赛事在周日举办且有两对兄弟分拆对抗，均为史上首次。剑桥队赛艇比赛两天前与快艇相撞导致换下一人，剑桥大学戈尔迪赛艇俱乐部在预备赛战胜牛津大学伊西斯赛艇俱乐部，[[牛津剑桥女子赛艇对抗赛|女子赛事]]和男子主赛一样是牛津队胜出。

== 背景 ==
[[File:Boat_Race_2015_-_Boris_Rankov.jpg|right]]

[[牛津剑桥赛艇对抗赛|牛津剑桥赛艇对抗赛]]是[[牛津大学|牛津大学]]（又称“深蓝”）和[[剑桥大学|剑桥大学]]（又称“浅蓝”）1829年开始举办的[[赛艇|并排赛艇]]比赛<ref name="blues">{{cite web | url = https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2003/apr/06/theobserver | newspaper = [[觀察家報|The Observer]] | title = Dark Blues aim to punch above their weight | date = 2003-04-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190408071418/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2003/apr/06/theobserver | archive-date = 2019-04-08 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-03-14 }}</ref>，在[[泰晤士河|泰晤士河]]位于西南伦敦[[帕特尼|帕特尼]]至[[摩特雷克|摩特雷克]]的6.8公里[[冠军水道|冠军水道]]举行<ref>{{cite web | access-date = 2021-03-14 | date = 2014-03-25 | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/destinations/europe/united-kingdom/england/london/articles/University-Boat-Race-2014-spectators-guide/ | newspaper = [[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] | title = University Boat Race 2014: spectators' guide | last = Smith | archive-date = 2020-10-20 | dead-url = no | first = Oliver | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201020103141/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/destinations/europe/united-kingdom/england/london/articles/University-Boat-Race-2014-spectators-guide/ }}</ref>。比赛是两所大学的重大荣誉项目，引来英国和世界各地媒体争相报道<ref name="CBC">{{cite news | title = Former Winnipegger in winning Oxford–Cambridge Boat Race crew | date = 2014-04-06 | publisher = CBC News | access-date = 2020-09-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200918213314/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manitoba/former-winnipegger-in-winning-oxford-cambridge-boat-race-crew-1.2600176 | archive-date = 2020-09-18 | dead-url = no | url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manitoba/former-winnipegger-in-winning-oxford-cambridge-boat-race-crew-1.2600176 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://theboatrace.org/men/tv-and-radio | title = TV and radio | publisher = The Boat Race Company Limited | access-date = 2014-10-06 | archive-date = 2014-10-06 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006123036/http://theboatrace.org/men/tv-and-radio}}</ref>。卫冕冠军牛津队[[2002年牛津剑桥赛艇对抗赛|上一年]]以0.75倍艇长优势夺冠<ref name="results">{{cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201123215158/https://www.theboatrace.org/results | dead-url = no | url = https://theboatrace.org/results | archive-date = 2020-11-23 | publisher = The Boat Race Company Limited | title = Boat Race – Results | access-date = 2021-03-14}}</ref>，但剑桥队历史上共有77次胜出，牛津队70次，另外[[1877年牛津剑桥赛艇对抗赛|1877年]]双方战平<ref>{{Cite web | access-date = 2021-03-22 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200922130142/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/specials/boat_race_2002/1900453.stm | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/specials/boat_race_2002/1900453.stm | title = Oxford clinch Boat Race | date = 2002-03-30 | publisher = BBC Sport | archive-date = 2020-09-22}}</ref><ref name="classic">{{cite web | title = Classic moments – the 1877 dead heat | access-date = 2014-10-06 | url = http://theboatrace.org/men/classic-moments-the-1877-dead-heat | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006125353/http://theboatrace.org/men/classic-moments-the-1877-dead-heat | archive-date = 2014-10-06 | publisher = The Boat Race Company Limited }}</ref>。本届赛事是[[安本资产管理|安本资产管理]]连续第四年赞助<ref name="blues" />，也是史上首次在周日举办，避免和[[2003年英国国家障碍赛马大赛|2003年英国国家障碍赛马大赛]]的电视直播撞车<ref name="classic" /><ref>{{Cite web | newspaper = [[獨立報|The Independent]] | first = Christopher | last = Dodd | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/general/rowing-boat-race-enters-new-waters-with-sunday-evening-slot-5352884.html | date = 2003-06-04 | title = Rowing: Boat Race enters new waters with Sunday evening slot | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150925223353/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/general/rowing-boat-race-enters-new-waters-with-sunday-evening-slot-539677.html | archive-date = 2015-09-25 | access-date = 2021-03-22 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[1984年牛津剑桥赛艇对抗赛|1984年比赛]]原定周日举行，但因剑桥队赛艇与驳船相撞推迟<ref>{{Cite news | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/general/boat-race-crash-puts-cambridge-crew-plans-in-doubt-113804.html | title = Crash puts Cambridge crew plans in doubt | first = Christoper | last = Dodd | date = 2003-04-05 | newspaper = The Independent | page = 12 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304202804/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/general/boat-race-crash-puts-cambridge-crew-plans-in-doubt-113804.html | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | accessdate = 2021-03-23 }}</ref>。

首届[[牛津剑桥女子赛艇对抗赛|牛津剑桥女子赛艇对抗赛]]1927年举行，20世纪60年代成为年度赛事，2014年才纳入[[亨利赛艇对抗赛|亨利赛艇对抗赛]]。女子赛事也在泰晤士河举办，与男子比赛和预备赛在同一天。<ref>{{cite web | access-date = 2014-10-06 | url = http://theboatrace.org/women/history | dead-url = yes | archive-date = 2014-10-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006112628/http://theboatrace.org/women/history | title = A brief history of the Women's Boat Race | publisher = The Boat Race Company Limited }}</ref>牛津大学伊西斯赛艇俱乐部和剑桥大学戈尔迪赛艇俱乐部从1965年开始举办预备赛，通常是男子赛艇对抗赛前在[[潮汐水道_(泰晤士河)|潮汐水道]]举行<ref name="results" />。

本届比赛裁判鲍里斯·兰科夫（{{lang|en|Boris Rankov}}）是前牛津队划手，曾于1978至1983年代表深蓝队连续参加六届比赛，创下个人连续参赛次数纪录<ref>{{Cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181015080159/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/olympics/rowing/5062749/60-Second-Interview-Boris-Rankov-Boat-Race-Umpire.html | archive-date = 2018-10-15 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/olympics/rowing/5062749/60-Second-Interview-Boris-Rankov-Boat-Race-Umpire.html | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | title = 60 Second Interview: Boris Rankov, Boat Race Umpire | first = Gareth A. | last = Davies | access-date = 2021-03-22 | date = 2009-03-27 }}</ref>。教练[[罗宾·威廉姆斯_(划船教练)|罗宾·威廉姆斯]]（{{lang|en|Robin Williams}}）第九次带领剑桥队参赛<ref name="recharge">{{Cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304214003/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/general/rowing-the-recharging-of-the-light-blue-brigade-123987.html | title = The recharging of the Light Blue brigade | newspaper = The Independent | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/general/rowing-the-recharging-of-the-light-blue-brigade-123987.html | access-date = 2021-03-22 | date = 2003-01-12 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，牛津队教练是肖恩·鲍登（{{lang|en|Sean Bowden}}）<ref name="rely">{{Cite web | newspaper = The Independent | access-date = 2021-03-22 | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/general/rowing-boat-race-crews-rely-on-league-of-nations-122231.html | title = Rowing: Boat race crews rely on league of nations | first = Christopher | last = Dodd | date = 2003-03-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201646/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/general/rowing-boat-race-crews-rely-on-league-of-nations-122231.html | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，另有舵手顾问[[丹尼尔·托波斯基|丹尼尔·托波斯基]]（{{lang|en|Daniel Topolski}}）协助<ref>{{Cite news | title = Oxford forced to fight rough water | first = Robert Treharne | last = Jones | date = 2003-04-03 | newspaper = The Times | access-date = 2021-03-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150928140643/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/sport/article2234570.ece | dead-url = no | url = https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/oxford-forced-to-fight-rough-water-fs3m6lltvjx | archive-date = 2015-09-28 }}</ref>。

== 选手 ==
比赛两天前，剑桥队首选船首韦恩·波门（{{lang|en|Wayne Pommen}}）在练习时赛艇与港监的快艇全速相撞导致手腕骨折<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/boat_race_2003/2918817.stm | title = Cambridge bowman breaks wrist | date = 2003-04-05 | access-date = 2021-03-22 | publisher = BBC Sport | archive-date = 2022-03-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220318132456/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/boat_race_2003/2918817.stm }}</ref>。马蒂亚斯·克莱因兹（{{lang|en|Matthias Kleinz}}）撞到头但无需就医<ref name="highanddry">{{Cite news | title = Pommen injured as collision leaves Cambridge high and dry | first = John | last = Goodbody | date = 2003-04-05 | url = https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/pommen-injured-as-collision-leaves-cambridge-high-and-dry-dtrnkp0sm5s | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2015-11-21 | access-date = 2021-03-22 | newspaper = The Times | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151121060841/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/sport/article2234601.ece }}</ref>。剑桥队七号队员詹姆斯·利文斯顿（{{lang|en|James Livingston}}）表示：“我有一会儿以为自己没命了，当时大家就要全力以赴，突然我听到吉姆（指詹姆斯·奥马提安）大叫。我从没听过谁那么害怕的声音”<ref name="die">{{Cite news | title = Light Blue crew feared for his life | newspaper = The Guardian | page = 28 | first = Martin | last = Cross | date = 2003-04-05}}</ref>。波门表示赛前发生这么大的事故实在令人失望，但“蹲在角落生闷气什么用都没有”<ref>{{Cite news | title = Oarsman is thrown in at deep end | first = Andrew | last = Longmore | date = 2003-04-06 | url = https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/rowing-oarsman-is-thrown-in-at-deep-end-jnw7jpsjnnb | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304044229/http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/sport/article46168.ece | newspaper = The Sunday Times | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | access-date = 2021-03-22 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。事故导致三只船浆损毁，两套索具撞弯，赛艇送到[[韦布里奇|韦布里奇]]修理<ref>{{Cite news | title = Crash puts Cambridge crew plans in doubt | first = Christopher | last = Dodd | page = 12 | newspaper = The Independent | date = 2003-04-05}}</ref>。本·史密斯（{{lang|en|Ben Smith}}）取代波门上场，他的亲兄弟马修（{{lang|en|Matthew}}）是牛津队尾桨手<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/2399147/Cambridge-lose-bowman.html | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | title = Cambridge lose bowman | date = 2003-04-05 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160229063831/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/2399147/Cambridge-lose-bowman.html | archive-date = 2016-02-29 | access-date = 2021-03-22 }}</ref>。自[[1979年牛津剑桥赛艇对抗赛|1979年]]以来，这还是各方首次这么晚变更参赛阵营<ref>{{Cite news | title = Cambridge face nervous wait after collision | first = Rachel | last = Quarrell | page = 14 | date = 2003-04-05 | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph}}</ref>。詹姆斯·利文斯顿的亲兄弟戴维（{{lang|en|David}}）是牛津队选手，加上史密斯兄弟便有两对兄弟分拆对抗，这在牛津剑桥赛艇对抗赛历史上也是首次<ref>{{Cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161220214029/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/general/rowing-james-gives-light-blues-a-fresh-look-as-brotherhood-rules-waves-113924.html | archive-date = 2016-12-20 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/general/rowing-james-gives-light-blues-a-fresh-look-as-brotherhood-rules-waves-113924.html | newspaper = The Independent | title = James gives Light Blues a fresh look as brotherhood rules waves | first = Nick | last = Townsend | date = 2003-04-06 | access-date = 2021-03-22 }}</ref>。

4月1日，选手在[[倫敦眼|倫敦眼]]正式称重<ref>{{Cite news | title = Umpire tells coxes to steer clear of clashes | newspaper = The Times | first = Mike | last = Rosewell | date = 2003-04-01 | archive-date = 2015-11-21 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151121052257/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/sport/article2234553.ece | url = https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/umpire-tells-coxes-to-steer-clear-of-clashes-mn6gg5md9s7 | accessdate = 2021-03-22 }}</ref>。剑桥队平均每人要轻七公斤<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/photo_galleries/2906725.stm | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200628210826/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/photo_galleries/2906725.stm | dead-url = no | title = Crews weigh in | date = 2003-04-01 | access-date = 2021-03-22 | publisher = BBC Sport | archive-date = 2020-06-28 }}</ref>，是[[1990年牛津剑桥赛艇对抗赛|1990年]]后最大的体重差距，也是[[1975年牛津剑桥赛艇对抗赛|1975年]]后深蓝队体重最轻的一次<ref>{{Cite news | title = History weighs on Oxford | first = Rachel | last = Quarrell | date = 2003-04-02 | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | page = 8}}</ref>。媒体认为牛津队此赛获胜无望<ref name="highanddry" /><ref>{{Cite web | title = Rowing: Acer in the pack inspires Oxford's Boat Race crew | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/general/others/rowing-acer-in-the-pack-inspires-oxford-s-boat-race-crew-8555312.html | newspaper = The Independent | last = Simon | date = 2013-03-31 | access-date = 2021-03-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305035152/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/general/others/rowing-acer-in-the-pack-inspires-oxfords-boat-race-crew-8555312.html | first = Nik | archive-date = 2016-03-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。剑桥队平均23岁，牛津队21岁。牛津队包括英国人七名，澳大利亚和加拿大人各一名；剑桥队英国人四名，美国和德国人各两名，澳大利亚人一名<ref>{{Cite web | access-date = 2021-03-22 | publisher = BBC Sport | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200628210625/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/boat_race_2003/2843477.stm | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/boat_race_2003/2843477.stm | title = Meet the Oxford University team | archive-date = 2020-06-28 | dead-url = no | date = 2003-03-31 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200628210638/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/boat_race_2003/2842665.stm | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/boat_race_2003/2842665.stm | title = Meet the Cambridge University team | date = 2003-03-31 | access-date = 2021-03-22 | publisher = BBC Sport | archive-date = 2020-06-28 }}</ref>。30岁的剑桥队尾桨手蒂姆·伍格（{{lang|en|Tim Wooge}}）已是第三次参加牛津剑桥赛艇对抗赛<ref name="recharge" />，是两队最重的选手<ref name="highanddry" />，还是[[剑桥大学赛艇俱乐部|剑桥大学赛艇俱乐部]]史上首位德裔主席<ref name="rely" />。牛津队尾桨手马修·史密斯第四次参加比赛<ref name="rely" />。[[罗宾·伯恩-泰勒|罗宾·伯恩-泰勒]]（{{lang|en|Robin Bourne-Taylor}}）、巴西尔·迪克森（{{lang|en|Basil Dixon}}）与马修·史密斯都是牛津队2002年赛事划手，剑桥队只有詹姆斯·利文斯顿曾参加上一年比赛<ref>{{Cite news | title = Weight of history in favour of Light Blues | first = John | last = Goodbody | date = 2003-04-02 | newspaper = The Times | access-date = 2021-03-22 | url = https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/weight-of-history-in-favour-of-light-blues-rqxrkmvm7gl | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151121055434/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/sport/article2234564.ece | archive-date = 2015-11-21 }}</ref>。
