== 比赛详情 ==

=== 主赛 ===
[[File:Boat_Race_at_Barnes_Bridge_2003_-_Oxford_winners.jpg|right]]时牛津队（选手身穿深赛服装）略为领先]]

剑桥队[[擲硬幣|擲硬幣]]胜出，赛艇俱乐部主席伍格大声宣布：“剑桥选择萨里侧”<ref name="Livingston">{{Cite book | title = Blood Over Water | first1 = David | first2 = James | last = Livingston1 | last2 = Livingston | publisher = Bloomsbury Publishing | year = 2010 | isbn= 978-1-4088-0119-2 | pages = 236, 255, 263}}</ref>。剑桥队选中泰晤士河南岸（“萨里侧”）为起点，牛津队在北侧（“米德尔塞克斯侧”）<ref name="bbc">{{Cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210309143726/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/boat_race_2003/2921361.stm | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/boat_race_2003/2921361.stm | title = Oxford win Boat Race | publisher = BBC Sport | access-date = 2021-03-22 | date = 2003-04-12 | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。比赛开始时是阴天，清风徐来水波不兴<ref name="asit">{{Cite web | publisher = BBC Sport | date = 2003-04-06 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/boat_race_2003/2922123.stm | archive-date = 2020-10-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201022200757/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/other_sports/boat_race_2003/2922123.stm | dead-url = no | title = The Boat Race: as it happened | access-date = 2021-03-22 }}</ref>。牛津队划桨速度略超对手，早期领先剑桥队，裁判警告双方舵手避免划桨碰撞。深蓝队领先半秒抵达迈尔点（{{lang|en|Mile Post}}）<ref name="rowingnews">{{cite news | pages = 7, 26–27 | access-date = 2021-03-22 | work = Rowing News | first = Christopher | last = Dodd | date = 2003-05-04 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=WksEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA7&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | title = Features – 2003 Boat Race}}</ref>。比赛开始五分钟时，领先三分之一艇长的牛津队再受裁判警告避免碰桨后开始偏离线路，剑桥队在双方多次碰桨后领先，早一秒经过[[漢默史密斯橋|漢默史密斯橋]]<ref name="rowingnews" />。接下来通向奇斯威克台阶（{{lang|en|Chiswick Steps}}）的长长弯道剑桥一直领先，牛津在后咬紧不放，直到逼近[[巴恩斯铁路桥|巴恩斯铁路桥]]、水道弯向有利一面后再度领先<ref name="rowingnews" />。牛津通过巴恩斯铁路桥时领先四分之三个艇长，剑桥追上三分之一个艇长，此后每一次划桨都追上一点点直到冲刺<ref name="rowingnews" />，但深蓝对还是以约30厘米优势率先通过终点，是牛津剑桥赛艇对抗赛历史上最小的获胜优势<ref name="asit" /><ref>{{Cite web | url = http://theboatrace.org/men/classic-moments-the-closest-race | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141008204926/http://theboatrace.org/men/classic-moments-the-closest-race | archive-date = 2014-10-08 | title = Classic moments – The closest race | publisher = The Boat Race Company Limited | access-date = 2014-10-08 }}</ref>。

牛津队的成绩是18分6秒<ref name="bbc" />。兰科夫没有马上宣布结果，而是“张开双臂耸耸肩”<ref name="closest">{{Cite news | title = Oxford survive the closest of calls | first = John | last = Goodbody | date = 2003-04-07 | newspaper = The Times | access-date = 2021-03-23 | url = https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/oxford-survive-the-closest-of-calls-mnxrhrrc69s | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151121052619/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/sport/article2234628.ece | archive-date = 2015-11-21 }}</ref>。终点裁判本·肯特（{{lang|en|Ben Kent}}）向兰科夫确认赛果，胜方优势约0.05秒<ref name="epic">{{Cite news | title = Oxford's epic victory closer than 'dead heat' | date = 2003-04-07 | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/olympics/rowing/2399264/Rowing-Oxfords-epic-victory-closer-than-dead-heat.html | page = 12 | first = Rachel | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180221163613/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/olympics/rowing/2399264/Rowing-Oxfords-epic-victory-closer-than-dead-heat.html | archive-date = 2018-02-21 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-03-23 | last = Quarrell | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph }}</ref>，兰科夫在[[奇西克桥|奇西克桥]]下向参赛选手宣布结果：“牛津队领先一英尺”<ref>{{Cite news | title = Spirit of 1963 sees dark blues through | first = Martin | last = Cross | newspaper = The Guardian | page = 18 | date = 2003-04-07 | url = https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2003/apr/07/3 | access-date = 2021-03-23 | archive-date = 2016-12-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161202015916/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2003/apr/07/3 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。詹姆斯·利文斯顿的著作自承当时眼睛用力睁大、太阳穴鼓起，队友都非常难受<ref name="Livingston" />。

胜方平均每人比对手重七公斤，此前历届比赛还从未出现平均体重超对手6.4公斤后仍能获胜<ref>{{Cite news | title = Oxford overcome weight of history – by 12 inches | first = Paul | last = Weaver | page = 18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161202015917/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2003/apr/07/highereducation.students | date = 2003-04-07 | url = https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2003/apr/07/highereducation.students | newspaper = The Guardian | archive-date = 2016-12-02 | access-date = 2021-03-23 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。这是牛津过去四年第三次胜利，把双方历史总比分追到71比77<ref name="results" />。按照传统，牛津队在终点把舵手阿克尔·纳瑟科特（{{lang|en|Acer Nethercott}}）抛到水里庆祝<ref>{{Cite web | access-date = 2021-03-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924043300/http://www.gettyimages.co.uk/detail/news-photo/the-victorious-oxford-cox-acer-nethercott-is-thrown-in-the-news-photo/1955290 | archive-date = 2015-09-24 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.gettyimages.co.uk/detail/news-photo/the-victorious-oxford-cox-acer-nethercott-is-thrown-in-the-news-photo/1955290 | title = The victorious Oxford Cox Acer Nethercott is thrown in the Thames in traditional manner... | publisher = Getty Images }}</ref>。

=== 预备赛和女子赛 ===
剑桥大学戈尔迪俱乐部在预备赛以九倍艇长的显著优势战胜牛津大学伊西斯俱乐部，用时18分4秒，比对手快两秒<ref name="bbc" />，是过去七年第六次胜利，也是连续第四次胜利<ref name="asit" />。牛津队以6分35秒赢得第58届女子赛事，领先对手3.5倍艇长，是该队连续第二年获胜，历史总比分追到20比38<ref name="results" /><ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/olympics/rowing/2398883/Rowing-Oxford-show-way.html | title = Oxford show way | first = Rachel | last = Quarrell | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | access-date = 2021-03-23 | date = 2003-04-01 | archive-date = 2016-02-29 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160229095645/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/olympics/rowing/2398883/Rowing-Oxford-show-way.html }}</ref>。

